{"tid":292297,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港台: 新教育副局長蔡若蓮 現任福建中學校長  初中班級全以「普教中」授課","createTime":"2017-06-21T09:12:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-21T09:46:19.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a0119b106fcfefa46ea4e5b72e9e569949c552","tid":292297,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:12:12.000Z","msg":"消息指，教聯會副主席蔡若蓮有機會出任教育局副局長。現任福建中學(小西灣)校長的蔡若蓮，學校所有初中班級均以「普教中」授課。<br />\n<br />\n去年立法會選舉出選教育界功能組別失敗，如今有消息指將出任副局長。曾在節目中指「普通話教語文有優勢」，蔡若蓮強調普通話的重要，但「普通話與廣東話不是對立」。教育局研普教中十年仍無定論，未知新班子會否帶來改變。<br />\n重溫2016年《視點31》的討論環節。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/1154319304714566/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Frthk31thisweek%2Fvideos%2F1154319304714566%2F&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=5cfd98ba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/rthk31thisweek/videos/1154319304714566/</a>"},{"pid":"73eb12992a735f208bed3d3a7e1883ad00e7401b","tid":292297,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"簡短版: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/videos/1019173781472680/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2Fvideos%2F1019173781472680%2F&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=d137ebc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/videos/1019173781472680/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前《視點31》上有進步教師同盟召集人施安娜老師，同教聯會副主席蔡若蓮討論普通話教中文嘅成效，高下立見。節目一開始問蔡副主席「普教中」嘅成效如何，佢就顧左右而言他；後來就話唔應該唔顧普通話學習。施老師就直斥其非，指「無人話反對普通話教學」，篤破偷換概念嘅技倆；並且透露消息，指教育局無發佈二千至零六年研究報告，係因為報告證明普教中學童高階思維能力更差，不利當局「普教中」嘅發展方向。環環精彩，所以本會謹作兩分鐘節錄，加以字幕，俾市民廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhongkonglangstudies%2F&d=JCnWpoNFTYXb1hSje%2B7cQAKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=a2010830\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hongkonglangstudies/</a>"},{"pid":"9edc98c52f56f1bce4bdbe4f35b5735660686723","tid":292297,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:16:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"436d5df1a6b475542a298563b87ffceee745e6df","tid":292297,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:22:44.000Z","msg":"又係呢條垃圾"},{"pid":"58cb6a9a1b9b174bbba19a4a705e582ab3f9a31e","tid":292297,"uid":24781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"條八婆老是常出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7447e2ba89d2d0cceac745e397bedb4bf98bea96","tid":292297,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:33:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係呢條垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數有外國籍，或者冚家移左民"},{"pid":"047c461e5a394c6ad420343bc4116e772ea5010b","tid":292297,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係呢條垃圾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數有外國籍，或者冚家移左民</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n仔女一係出國一係國際學校<br />\n<br />\n自己就推普教中俾港豬嘆"},{"pid":"2b637be6e99d5896957d41b17cf9fab137c6fe87","tid":292297,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"唔好害啲小朋友啦屌妳老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042beac7551c29ada5492410d9c9ddcb4b77fdb6","tid":292297,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"[摑選民一巴]傳任教育局副局長 教聯會福建中學蔡若蓮敗選立法會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/292281/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/292281/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ffaba66f2abb9c6db649ccc7cf514db0275321ce","tid":292297,"uid":498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:46:19.000Z",